msgid "mission.object.salvager.name"
msgstr "Scrapper"

msgid "mission.object.salvager.info"
msgstr "A resource gathering ship. Collects [SCRAP] and [DEBRIS]."

msgid "mission.object.salvager.build"
msgstr "These salvage ships, colloquially known as Scrappers, are essential to all space missions. They are equipped to deconstruct all types of space debris, even from destroyed enemy ships. These ships are of a basic design, however, and are unable to defend themselves and have limited storage. The IEE recommends that squadrons to keep them away from battles."
